{
  "texts": [
    "Discerning the precise factors or linguistic cues that drive propaganda detection can be challenging, thus hindering insights into the underlying mechanisms.",
    "Future research avenues may explore incremental or lifelong learning methods for training the H-GIN model.",
    "Enabling continuous adaptation to new propaganda instances would help tackle evolving techniques and ensure a more robust detection system.",
    "For more deep learning tasks, it is recommended to review several studies, such as query response 71, neural network algorithms [72] [73] [74], and recent advancements in model architectures, such as transformers and GANs.",
    "This can provide insights into optimizing the performance and understanding state-of-the-art techniques."
  ]
}